<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>بن يسار عن أبيه <span class="c2">(أنه)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> كره <span class="c2">(التروح)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> في الصلاة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
